title: 3 Metaverse Stocks to Buy Right Now
description: The metaverse may feel far off, but investors may want to pay close attention to what some of the world's leading technology companies are doing in this space.  Amazon (NASDAQ: AMZN), Apple (NASDAQ: AAPL), and Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) are poised to benefit from it as it grows.  Amazon may seem like an odd choice on this list, but the virtual worlds will require lots of cloud computing power, and Amazon Web Services (AWS) has it in spades.
